Great upload, thanks for putting all episodes in one torrent! Saves a lot of trouble trying to find each season individually. I remember watching a lot of these episodes on SyFy, but there's many I haven't seen.
@cuffofizz
Seems almost too obvious to say, but if you want to watch these on your DVD player but save discs, make sure you have a player able to play avi files, then make data discs. I did that with the X-Files and fit about 12 eps per disc. Depends on the size of the files.
